{"id":"812542663708590080","type":"text","timestamp":1774901069,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/812542663708590080","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/tiny-foxgirl-daddy/806459511035576320\">tiny-foxgirl-daddy</a>:</p><blockquote><p>Sometimes I see a cute girl and think to myself, “being a lesbian is pretty neat.”</p><p>Then I remember that trans lesbians exist.</p><p>And then I&rsquo;m like &ldquo;actually being a lesbian is fucking awesome!&rdquo;</p></blockquote>","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"tiny-foxgirl-daddy"},"post":{"id":"806459511035576320"}}],"baseline_notes":62,"baseline_ts":1774916064.964}